verbose_text: MTX significantly decreased the amount of tGSH in the MTXG group (1.6 +/-0.3 mg/L) compared to the HREM, HREG, and HG groups (P < 0.001), while the amount of tGSH was found to be significantly higher in the HREM group (11.8 +/-2.3 mg/L, 12.3 +/-1.9 mg/L) compared to the HG group (9.2 +/-0.5 mg/L; P < 0.01) (XREF_FIG).
